text:
This patch eliminates bug in HTTP tag IO tag library. The bug appears then
one set attribute ACTION tag HTTP to POST. Tag HTTP doesn't invoke method
POST instead of it invokes method GET. After applying this patch tag HTTP
can invoke method POST.

